ReaPack is a package manager for REAPER, the Digital Audio Workstation.

Discover,
[install](//reacomics.tumblr.com/post/153946589700/033-reapack-feedback){:rel="nofollow"
.egg} and keep up to date your REAPER resources including ReaScripts, JS
effects, extensions, themes, language packs, templates, web interfaces and more.

{:.screenshot}
![Screenshot of ReaPack](/images/package-browser.png)

## Main features

- Easy access to 1,200+ packages from the default repositories
- Import third-party repositories to get more content
- Install/update in batch or pick only what you need
- Decentralized by design, free to use and open-source
- Documentation display for packages and repositories
- Opt-in setting to test pre-release packages
- Import/export sets of installed packages offline
- And a lot more...

